Face Scan
Please read these terms and conditions carefully before using our face scan function for vital health parameter analysis. By using this service, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following terms and conditions:
1. Consent and Authorization
By using our face scan service, you consent to the collection and analysis of your facial data for the purpose of identifying health parameters, including heart rate, stress level, oxygen saturation, and more.
2. Data Privacy and Security
We prioritise the privacy and security of your data. Your facial scan data will be stored securely and treated in accordance with our privacy policy.
3. Accuracy of Results
The health parameter results generated by the face scan are for informational purposes only. They should not be considered a substitute for professional medical advice. Consult a healthcare professional for any health concerns.
The health parameter results generated by a face scan are based on a variety of factors, including the person`s age, gender, ethnicity, and facial features. These results can be used to estimate a person`s overall health, but they should not be considered a substitute for professional medical advice
Star health allied insurance and co. is not liable for any damages arising from the use of any results.
4. Age Restriction
This service is intended for individuals aged 18 and above. If you are under 18, please do not use this service.
5. Data Retention
We will retain your facial scan data for as outlined in our privacy policy to show the user for scan history.
6. Limited Liability
We do not assume any liability for the accuracy, completeness, or usefulness of the health parameter results obtained through this service.
7. Consent Revocation
You have the right to withdraw your consent at any time. To do so, please contact our customer support.
8. Compliance with Laws
You agree to use this service in compliance with all applicable laws and regulations in your jurisdiction.
9. Updates and Modifications
These terms and conditions may be updated or modified at our discretion. Please check this page periodically for any changes.
10. Contact Information
For questions or concerns about these terms and conditions or our face scanning service, please contact our customer support. By using our face scan service, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to these terms and conditions
11. Non-Medical Disclaimer
This is a software/AI based assessment and should not be used as a substitute for professional medical advice.